d, meaningful action space."}, {"problem": "Generic visual pretraining may not yield features aligned with manipulation progress or downstream control.", "method": "Pretrain/finetune the visual encoder via affordance learning (VRB), then freeze it for behavior cloning on Franka Kitchen tasks and assess goal-distance in feature space during execution. The affordance-pretrained encoder outperforms R3M on BC success rates and produces feature distances that decrease monotonically with task progress, indicating more control-relevant representations."}]}
